  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Walking holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093530/close-up-feet.png?width=500&amp;height=280.68965517241384" alt="how we grade our walks" data-udi="umb://media/ada05f0bc8de4c3d84cb81a1965dba1d" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">No need to second-guess yourself when it comes to selecting the perfect walking holiday - we've got everything covered. Our grading system is based on our recommendations and expertise from our UK and overseas teams. We’ve highlighted what resorts are best for easy, moderate and challenging walks, taking into account every aspect of the walks from the terrain to the elevation changes. So lace up those boots and get ready to explore the outdoors with confidence.</span></p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Easy walking</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093748/easy-her0.png?width=500&amp;height=261.3793103448276" alt="easy walking" data-udi="umb://media/d271ea268e76474799bc83698a2d69a5" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re looking for an easy walk, our resorts with flatter rails and gentle terrain are your go-to:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">You’ll have a bunch of shorter walks to choose from, some as short as five kilometres</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Some resorts have lifts or public transport that’ll take you straight to the good views. </span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are usually plenty of places to stop and take a breather along the way.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Recommended resorts for easy walking</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7cb79dd08b1944be915c6b815ba4120d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cb79dd08b1944be915c6b815ba4120d}" title="La Clusaz">La Clusaz</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae}" title="Zell am See">Zell am See</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken">Interlaken</a> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Moderate walking</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093751/moderate-walking-holidays.png?width=500&amp;height=261.3793103448276" alt="moderate walking" data-udi="umb://media/977997056b514ebea4571c9e7299e180" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Expect varied trails in resorts that are great for moderate walks:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">There are plenty of routes between five and ten kilometres with a generally easier terrain and some ascents and descents.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">In some resorts you can use the lift network or public transport for part of the journey. </span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Most trails will have places to stop and rest, or even grab some lunch.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Recommended resorts for moderate walking</strong></p>
<p><span class="ui-provider gp b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak"><a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo">Lake Iseo</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/4cead924140a465fa8868775d321e171" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4cead924140a465fa8868775d321e171}" title="Montecatini" data-anchor="#">Montecatini</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0}" title="Lake Annecy">Lake Annecy</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel">Kitzbuhel</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/08db820246524b63b3bfadde3a69e4f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/08db820246524b63b3bfadde3a69e4f2}" title="Kandersteg">Kandersteg</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/085c5cbb87794e7c9ca8a69475a257df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/085c5cbb87794e7c9ca8a69475a257df}" title="Soll">Soll</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Challenging walking</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093746/challenging-hero.png?width=500&amp;height=261.3793103448276" alt="challenging walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/3ba12c494430493498ec0267c083c192" /></p>
<p>If you're ready for a challenge, we've got plenty of resorts to tempt you: <span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">There'll usually be plenty of longer hikes available of at least ten kilometres.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">They will likely have a more mountainous terrain with some steep ascents and descents and you'll need to have a good level of fitness and sure-footedness.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Recommended resorts for challenging walking</strong></p>
<p><span class="ui-provider gp b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak"><a data-udi="umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6}" title="Cinque Terre">Cinque Terre</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae93f514436f422b8a051f43d7310e8e}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>All abilities</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093545/walking.png?width=500&amp;height=280.68965517241384" alt="walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/db390f5eafcc49a382689f02a846aefa" /></p>
<p>We also have resorts that are perfect for all walking abilities:</p>
<ul>
<li><span>If you want to challenge yourself one day and take it easy the next, or if you're just not sure what level is right for you, these resorts are ideal.</span></li>
<li><span>Many have hundreds of kilometres of walking trails and complete flexibility to do as little or as much as you like.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Recommended resorts for all abilities</strong></p>
<p><span class="ui-provider gp b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak"><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>  </div>
<div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Step into summer with Inghams</strong></h2>
<p><strong><img src="/media/13089493/our-holidays-838x220.jpg" alt="Step into Summer" data-udi="umb://media/b40cf9d23b4a4012aaed9b15dfdb0eab" /></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ With over 85 years of experience you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ You'll have the reassurance and expert guidance of our reps when in resort. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ <strong>New for 2023:</strong> enjoy two guided walks per week in selected resorts*.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️Flights from your choice of 15 regional airports, transfers and accommodation are included in your holiday.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
